  "title": "Marketing Executive",
  "description": "<p><p><strong>Job description</strong><br />1.Create and coordinate content for social media, email marketing, websites, and promotional materials<br />2.Conduct market research to identify customer trends, competitor activity, and new opportunities<br />3. Collaborate with sales, design, and external agencies to achieve marketing objectives<br />4.Assist in planning and executing product launches, events, and promotional activities<br />5.Support brand management and ensure consistent messaging across all platforms<br />6.Track, analyze, and report on campaign performance and ROI<br />7.Manage marketing budgets and timelines where required</p><p></p><p><strong>Preferred skill</strong><br />1.Excel in graphic design or content creation skills<br />2.Experience with marketing automation or CRM tools<br />3.Creative thinking and idea generation<br />4.Email marketing and newsletters<br />5.Knowledge of Google Analytics or similar reporting tools</p><h3></h3></p>",
